data.description: ***MOTIVATED SELLER OFFERING 10K in Sellers Concessions *** Welcome home to this traditional ranch style home has classic style brick-front, handcrafted stone  surrounding the 2-car garage & durable HARDIE PLANK siding made to protect and beautify the home. Enjoy the quiet & serene space of the front & rear covered LANAI with a serene view. As you move into the interior; you'll notice an OPEN AIRY concept with impressive spaced ceiling heights and cedar view flooring throughout. Contemporary finishes adorn this JUST LIKE NEW home; Shaker-style kitchen cabinetry throughout, chic lighting fixtures, granite & quartz surfaces, etc. The open kitchen offers STAINLESS STEEL appliances, a double bowl kitchen sink and granite countertops. The primary suite is light & bright with, double insulated windows and trey ceiling. The primary bathroom suite offers shimmer quartz double vanity countertops, ceramic flooring, ceramic surround tub & ceramic tile shower (separate) with a decorated MOSAIC shower band. Enjoy entertaining guests at the granite elongated countertops under the overall illuminating recessed lighting opened up to the spacious dining area.  Nestled in the charming town of Dallas with a quaint, historic downtown,  you'll enjoy shopping and entertainment.  Nearby Silver Comet Trails.
